/**
 * \defgroup	DEVICE_HAL	Device HAL
 * \brief	Device Hardware Abstraction Layer
 * \details
 *		This layer provides a unified API for gpio, uart, spi, iic, wireless network
 *	controller. You can use this API to operate these devices without knowing exactly
 *	what device it is based on,such as a DesignWare uart or other uart, if both
 *	the uart device drivers are implemented under this unified API.
 */


